  07 Oct 2012; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Drop maintainer due retirement, #274113

  20 Aug 2012; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> -droid-113-r1.ebuild,
  droid-113-r2.ebuild:
  Stabilise on all archs, remove older. Wrt bug#429112.

